{"tid":726241,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[7月新番Netflix已出]刃牙 バキ Baki   最凶死刑囚編 集中討論","createTime":"2018-07-02T08:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T12:46:07.000Z","uid":3020,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a63925cbc74d907627d536c05ca886d86a953d","tid":726241,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/162618_5a8d4ea7dc9912a4bbbb1bd85ccdc0db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F162618_5a8d4ea7dc9912a4bbbb1bd85ccdc0db.jpg&h=caa0ddce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n描述地下格鬥場的冠軍「範馬刃牙」及其父、冠有地上最強生命這一稱呼的「範馬勇次郎」還有作品中各格鬥家的熱血格鬥物語。這次推出的電視動畫將描繪在「最大淘汰賽篇」中地下鬥技場登場的戰士們，此外還有以五名死刑犯為中心的「最兇死刑犯篇」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集數：26<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"http://baki-anime.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbaki-anime.jp%2F&d=jS8%2Bm%2FJlAMZ5KT69m4BQAP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d43aebf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://baki-anime.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\nバキ 最凶死刑囚編：　第1話 「シンクロニシティ」<br />\n<a href=\"http://himado.in/439035\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimado.in%2F439035&d=jS8%2Bm%2FJlAMZ5KT69m4BQAP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=332b6fd6\" target=\"_blank\">http://himado.in/439035</a><br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=00nwsWLCDv4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D00nwsWLCDv4&d=jS8%2Bm%2FJlAMZ5KT69m4BQAP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=57e3bf09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=00nwsWLCDv4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDrtSBvmfHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVDrtSBvmfHE&d=jS8%2Bm%2FJlAMZ5KT69m4BQAP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5a7da27a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDrtSBvmfHE</a>"},{"pid":"4fc54ead72f4841e61527a2b212227fcc40c7dcc","